          <span>Distribution &amp; Wholesale</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/computer-accessories-software/" class="fbr-industry-card">
          <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/computer.jpg" alt="Computer Accessories" />
          <span>Computer Accessories</span>
