        <p>An online Inventory management and accounting software in Pakistan, specially designed for small and medium-sized businesses. It offers FREE 14 days trial.</p>
        <p>It includes all modules: <a href="/sales/">Sales</a>, <a href="/purchases/">Purchase</a>, <a href="/inventory/">Inventory</a>, Accounting, <a href="/manufacturing/">Manufacturing</a>, <a href="/point-of-sale/">POS (Point of Sales)</a>, Ledgers, Trial Balance, Aging Reports, Income Statement, and Balance Sheet. It also supports Multi-currencies.</p>
        <p>Log in online anytime, anywhere using Mac, PC, tablet or phone to get a real-time view of your business.</p>
        <div class="fbr-overview-cta">
