        </div>
        <div class="fbr-prod-card">
          <div class="fbr-prod-icon">🛒</div>
          <h3>Point of Sales</h3>
          <p>FBR Integration, Advanced Inventory Control, Intuitive Shortcut Keys, and Customizable Loyalty Programs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fbr-prod-card">
          <div class="fbr-prod-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Receivables &amp; Payables</h3>
          <p>Keep track of money you have to receive and need to pay. In one click, find who hasn't paid you yet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fbr-prod-card">
          <div class="fbr-prod-icon">🏦</div>
          <h3>Banking Activities</h3>
          <p>Add, manage and track payments received to your bank accounts. Manage every cash-in and cash-out in one place.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fbr-prod-card">
          <div class="fbr-prod-icon">🏷️</div>
          <h3>Barcode Designer &amp; Printing</h3>
